  lines:
  - speaker: 0
    text: "\u1EDC\u2026 th\xF4i v\xE0o \u0111i."
  - speaker: 1
    text: "Ehhh? D\u1EC5 v\u1EADy lu\xF4n h\u1EA3 Oniichan?"
  - speaker: 0
    text: "T\xF4i \u0111ang m\u1EC7t. C\u1EADu \u0111i nhanh \u0111i tr\u01B0\u1EDBc
      khi t\xF4i \u0111\u1ED5i \xFD."
  - speaker: 1
    text: YATTAAA~ arigatou oniichan!
  - speaker: 1
    text: "M\u1ED9t ng\xE0y n\xE0o \u0111\xF3 em s\u1EBD d\u1EABn oniichan t\u1EDBi
      qu\xE1n c\xE0 ph\xEA h\u1EA7u g\xE1i"
  - speaker: 1
    text: "\u1EDE \u0111\xF3 oniichan s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFt th\u1EBF n\xE0o l\xE0 s\u1EE9c
      m\u1EA1nh ph\xE9p thu\u1EADt th\u1EADt s\u1EF1 ><"
